        "en": "CDAR Process Condition Code",
        "fr": "Code condition processus CDAR"
      },
      "desc": {
        "en": "CDAR ProcessConditionCode (MDT-9) identifying the lifecycle\nevent reported by the Flow 6 message. The normalizer derives\nit from the (StatusLine.Key, Status.Type) pair; callers can\npre-set it to pin a specific code (e.g. when round-tripping\na parsed CDV)."
